  <summary date="2018-03-05T05:00:00Z" status="Introduced in Senate">Protecting Children From Identity Theft Act

This bill requires the&#160;Social Security Administration to develop a database to facilitate the&#160;verification of consumer information upon request by a certified financial institution. Such verification shall be provided only with the consumer's consent and in connection with a credit transaction. Users of the database shall pay system costs.</summary>
